    ('\\textbf{性质}: \\(\\kappa\\) 是唯一满足上述等式的值，且当 \\(p_0 < p_1\\)\n时，\\(\\theta^* \\in (p_0, p_1)\\)。由 KL 散度的严格凸性保证唯一性。',
     '\\textbf{Property}: \\(\\kappa\\) is the unique value satisfying the above equality, and when \\(p_0 < p_1\\),\n\\(\\theta^* \\in (p_0, p_1)\\). Uniqueness is guaranteed by the strict convexity of KL divergence.'),
    ('SCX 的精确渐近常数', 'Exact Asymptotic Constant of SCX'),
    ('\\textbf{注意}: \\(\\max\\)\n取的是渐近主导项。若两指数完全相等，两阶项均需保留（它们的和）；若不完全相等但差值在\n\\(O(1/\\sqrt{M})\\) 内，则两个项都贡献到常数中。此处写的是最坏情况常数。',
     '\\textbf{Note}: The \\(\\max\\)\ntakes the asymptotically dominant term. If the two exponents are exactly equal, both terms must be retained (their sum); if they are not exactly equal but the difference is within\n\\(O(1/\\sqrt{M})\\), both terms contribute to the constant. What is written here is the worst-case constant.'),
