    ('\\textbf{推导来源}: 最优 Bayes 检验使用阈值\n\\(\\tau = (1-\\eta)/\\eta\\)。对应的\n\\(\\theta_{\\text{Bayes}} = \\theta^* + \\frac{1}{M}\\frac{\\log((1-\\eta)/\\eta)}{D^*} + O(1/M^2)\\)。O(1/M)\n的阈值偏移通过指数产生 \\(((1-\\eta)/\\eta)^s\\) 的 O(1) 乘性因子，该因子在\nFPR 和 FNR 贡献中\\textbf{同时出现}（因 \\(s = |\\lambda_1^*|/D^*\\) 且\n\\(1-s = \\lambda_0^*/D^*\\)），证明见 Lemma E §3-4。',
     '\\textbf{Derivation source}: The optimal Bayes test uses threshold\n\\(\\tau = (1-\\eta)/\\eta\\). The corresponding\n\\(\\theta_{\\text{Bayes}} = \\theta^* + \\frac{1}{M}\\frac{\\log((1-\\eta)/\\eta)}{D^*} + O(1/M^2)\\). The O(1/M)\nthreshold shift produces an O(1) multiplicative factor \\(((1-\\eta)/\\eta)^s\\) through the exponent, and this factor appears\n\\textbf{simultaneously} in both FPR and FNR contributions (since \\(s = |\\lambda_1^*|/D^*\\) and\n\\(1-s = \\lambda_0^*/D^*\\)); the proof is in Lemma E §3-4.'),
    ('比较：简单阈值 vs 自适应阈值', 'Comparison: Simple Threshold vs Adaptive Threshold'),
